14</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B. C.)</date>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n112002.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Carthaginian,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀλαλατός</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:72\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.72</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also fem., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Φοίνισσαι νῆες</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:116\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.116</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:13:80\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.80</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n112002.3\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">φοῖνιξ</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ῑκος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">purple</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">crimson,</tr_> because the discovery and earliest use of this colour was ascribed to the Phoenicians, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:141\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.141</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:219\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.219</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:23:201\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.201</biblScope></bibl>, etc.:—hence, </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n112002.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> (fem. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φοίνισσα</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> (v. infr.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φοῖνιξ</foreign> as fem., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg011.perseus-grc1:815\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">815</biblScope> </bibl>), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">blood-bay,</tr_> of a horse, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:454\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.454</biblScope> </bibl>; of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">red</tr_> cattle, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φοίνισσα ἀγέλα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:205\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.205</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:25:128\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblSc