 lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φοινίκων . . τῶν καρπίμων οἱ μὲν ἄρρενες αἱ δὲ θήλειαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:2:6:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HP\">HP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.6.6</biblScope></bibl></cit>, but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱ ἀπὸ τῶν ἀρρένων πρὸς τοὺς θήλεις [βοήθειαι]</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:2:8:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.8.4</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n112002.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">palm-frond,</tr_> as a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">badge of victory,</tr_> Arist <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ MM\">MM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1196a36</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.723b</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸν φ. τινὶ ἀποδοῦναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1264.tlg001:3:175\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Chrysipp.Stoic.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.175</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n112002.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">date,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0539.tlg001:56J\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hellanic.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">56J.</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0521.tlg001:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Epich.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0410.tlg001:65\" 